Watch Thereese unbox and test all the products from this curated beauty set specially made for kids from Shu Shu & Sassy. 
Shu Shu & Sassy is a lifestyle brand from Korea that caters to children pampering essentials that are organic and/ made of naturally derived ingredients. Everything from the brand is safe for kids. 
Special thanks to @millennialmoms.asia for the wonderful gift and @pocketpigdiary for my Frozen 2 Top.
